            "value": "Grünes Licht - pushen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sleep, energy, and recovery are all stacked.%@ Attack the top set and look for a real rep or load PR on the anchor lift.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Schlaf, Energie und Regeneration stehen gut.%@ Greif den Top-Satz an und such beim Ankerlift nach einem echten Wiederholungs- oder Last-PR."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Warm up thoroughly - earn the intensity": {
