    "Stack recovery": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Regeneration stapeln"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You're not quite fresh and no workout is planned - that's a fit. Use the day to rebuild: sleep, food, and light movement.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du bist nicht ganz frisch und kein Workout ist geplant - das passt. Nutze den Tag zum Aufbauen: Schlaf, Essen und leichte Bewegung."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "20-30 min walk or mobility": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "20-30 min Spaziergang oder Mobility"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hit protein target": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Proteinziel treffen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Target 7h+ sleep tonight": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Heute Nacht 7 h+ Schlaf anpeilen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Warm-up sets matter - don't rush them": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aufwärmsätze zählen - nicht hetzen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cut last accessory set on sore muscles": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Letzten Zubehörsatz bei müden Muskeln streichen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cap workout at ~45 min": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Workout auf ~45 min begrenzen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hold load, stay ~1 RIR lighter than usual": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Last halten, ~1 RIR leichter als sonst bleiben"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Train, but tune it down": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Trainieren, aber runterregeln"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Recovery is mixed. Don't chase a PR today - anchor lifts at planned load, accessories trimmed. Quality > tonnage.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Regeneration ist gemischt. Heute keinen PR jagen - Ankerlifts mit geplanter Last, Zubehör gekürzt. Qualität > Tonnage."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Full recovery day": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Voller Erholungstag"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your body is telling you it needs time. Let it. Sleep, food, and walking will pay off more than anything else today.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dein Körper sagt, dass er Zeit braucht. Gib sie ihm. Schlaf, Essen und Gehen bringen heute mehr als alles andere."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Extra hour of sleep if possible": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wenn möglich eine Stunde extra schlafen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Protein + water first": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Protein + Wasser zuerst"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Drop working load ~15-20%": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Arbeitslast um ~15-20 % senken"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cut 1-2 accessory exercises": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "1-2 Zubehörübungen streichen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Keep workout under 40 min": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Workout unter 40 min halten"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If it still feels wrong - swap to mobility": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wenn es sich weiter falsch anfühlt - auf Mobility wechseln"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Movement, not a grind": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bewegung, kein Durchbeißen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Readiness is low. A short, lighter workout beats skipping outright - but do not push through pain or form breakdown. Bank the rep quality, not the intensity.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Readiness ist niedrig. Ein kurzes, leichteres Workout ist besser als komplett auszulassen - aber nicht durch Schmerz oder Formverlust pushen. Sichere Satzqualität, nicht Intensität."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Multiple systems are flagged. Let today be about recovery. You'll come back measurably stronger.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mehrere Signale sind belastet. Heute geht es um Erholung. Du kommst messbar stärker zurück."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You're ready - let's train": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du bist bereit - los trainieren"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Readiness is high and today's workout is waiting. Make it count.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Readiness ist hoch und dein Workout wartet. Mach es wertvoll."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Recovery comes first today": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Regeneration geht heute vor"
          }
        }
      }
    },
